This is the latest circuit info. I'm making two seperate boards, the Audio 
board, and the sweep board. It's an attempt to make smaller boards to get 
the price per board down to an affordable level when i have the made. If you 
use Windows(XP) Image and Fax viewer you can print the schematic out on one 
page, or you can use the Paint program to view it.

I need to get a life!!

(old) Frank
